{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266280/extras/Nebelmer_KeyArt_Vignettage_steam_2.png?t=1729498543\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266280/extras/DemoTitle_english.png?t=1729498543\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this demo version, explore a part of the vast open world that awaits you when the game is released. Try out the different moves that will be necessary for your progress, and discover one of the three available biomes: the Enchanted Forest. This prologue will introduce you to the captivating story of Nebelmer. Get ready for an unforgettable adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266280/extras/GifTitle_1.png?t=1729498543\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266280/extras/GIFNebelmer_1.gif?t=1729498543\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your surfing and flying stick to move through this world. As you progress in your journey, you will encounter new ways of moving, depending on your environment: jumping in a water geyser, bouncing off a jellyfish or flying in a bubble, this world will never cease to impress you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266280/extras/GifTitle_2_2.png?t=1729498543\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266280/extras/GIFNebelmer_2.gif?t=1729498543\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nebelmer is made up of three main biomes, each with its own unique atmosphere and locations. A pink forest of giant mushrooms, an icy canyon lit by anemones and a waterfall inhabited by flying jellyfish, nothing is impossible under the mist. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266280/extras/GifTitle_3_2.png?t=1729498543\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266280/extras/GIFNebelmer_3.gif?t=1729498543\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as Ixe, a young boy living in a remote mountain village. All around it, everything is shrouded in mist, and danger seems to lurk behind. It is said that an ancient creature named Kamaska created this barrier of mist to protect your village. Eager to explore and discover the world, Ixe can\u2019t stand still forever. Fortunately, old lady Granny will help you discover what really lies beneath the mist.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266280/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729498543","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266280/page.bg.jpg?t=1729498543","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266280/05ddf661bd206e43e9d79e133c8362cbad34e603/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729498543","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266280/05ddf661bd206e43e9d79e133c8362cbad34e603/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729498543","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Captions available","id":13}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266280/extras/Nebelmer_KeyArt_Vignettage_steam_2.png?t=1729498543\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266280/extras/DemoTitle_english.png?t=1729498543\" /></