ountain village. All around it, everything is shrouded in mist, and danger seems to lurk behind. It is said that an ancient creature named Kamaska created this barrier of mist to protect your village. Eager to explore and discover the world, Ixe can\u2019t stand still forever. Fortunately, old lady Granny will help you discover what really lies beneath the mist.</p>","developers":["Brume Studio"],"fullgame":{"appid":"3134810","name":"Nebelmer"},"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266280/header.jpg?t=1729498543","is_free":true,"legal_notice":"\u00a92024 Brume Studio. All rights reserved. Nebelmer \u00ae is a registered trademark of Brume Studio.","linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257060483,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257060483/movie480.mp4?t=1728317489","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257060483/movie_max.mp4?t=1728317489"},"name":"Reveal Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257060483/4b5ef74cd443a8855a6294773641bc147738883e/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1728317489","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257060483/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1728317489","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257060483/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1728317489"}}],"name":"Nebelmer Demo","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 8 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> GTX 1070-TI<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> Version 11<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 3 GB available space</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10<br></li><li><str